  "stem": "<p>The number of cats at an animal shelter, sorted by breed and fur color, is shown in the table.</p><figure class=\"table\"><table border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Breed</th><th>Dark fur</th><th>Light fur</th><th>Total</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Tabby</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">4</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">11</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">15</td></tr><tr><td>Persian</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">9</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">14</td></tr><tr><td>Maine Coon</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">14</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">22</td></tr><tr><td>Siamese</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">12</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">18</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Which breed has a dark-fur population that is closest to being 1/3 of the total population for that breed?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>Tabby</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<p>Persian</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "c",
      "content": "<p>Maine Coon</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "d",
      "content": "<p>Siamese</p>"
    }
